  <h3>About</h3>
  <p><span class="bold underline">What is this?</span></p>
  <p>ELO Kitty is a web app designed to give users the ability to share photos of their cats, vote on their favorite cats vs. other cats, and view other users's cats.</p>

  <p><span class="bold underline">Background</span></p>
  <p>Inspired by a final project at a web development bootcamp, the physicist Arpad Elo and his <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elo_rating_system">rating system</a>, my friends who are always sharing pictures of cats with me, and the story of Mark Zuckerberg's Facemash - I created ELO Kitty as a fun project.</p>
  <p>Our goal is to help users share their beloved cats and match them up against other cute cats from around the world, with a touch of friendly competition to see which cats are most loved by the community.</p>
  <p>Best of luck and happy voting!</p>

